replyTime":"2018-11-18T17:25:20.000Z","msg":"讀緊u睇學校counselling centre會唔會有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得自己就快到臨界點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n但窮撚無錢睇私家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"326f38291139251429bea401cc9c748269a03987","tid":901433,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c509a938fc01036576dea921ccc342d1a3ed7414","tid":901433,"uid":131492,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T17:25:20.000Z","msg":"讀緊u睇學校counselling centre會唔會有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得自己就快到臨界點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n但窮撚無錢睇私家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:50:09.000Z","msg":"揾iccmw"},{"pid":"dd6f7d0d5d0af7a0343b82a454fa1b22360b0041","tid":901433,"uid":195183,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:50:29.000Z","msg":"熱線求助方法<br />\n<br />\n若您現在想自殺，請停一停、等一等。先致電給我們，我們不是專業輔導員亦不是其他精神健康的專業人士 - 我們只是那些明白置身於痛苦中的你是怎樣一回事的人。<br />\n我們願意聽你的傾訴&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n請給我們來電 2389 2222 (24小時) 或 電郵給我們：touch@sbhk.org.hk(撒瑪利亞人收)<br />\n或 真心話室(網上聊天室)：<a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk%2F&d=0Q%2BRVLC9lal1CM9duEnSiQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=a122616c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/</a> (服務時間：晚上8時至凌晨1時)"},{"pid":"7ec3dcd25d7f4d7075b17927057990d1c889efd5","tid":901433,"uid":33618,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T01:22:38.000Z","msg":"其實生活喺香港，真係好容易有抑鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea9de285fbf2e905e737cbf882c7116336f83d3","tid":901433,"uid":131626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3a83a595dbf7fc1f10f8527ee1b1aaba584d8d6e","tid":901433,"ui